### PROBAR ROLES
### =========================
### 1. REGISTER USER (FREE)
### =========================
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "free@free.com",
  "username": "free",
  "password": "free",
  "dateOfBirth": "2004-11-29"
}

### =========================
### 2. LOGIN
### =========================
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "user7",
  "password": "1234"
}

### =========================
### 3. GET CURRENT USER (FREE)
### =========================
GET http://localhost:8080/api/users/currentUser
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### =========================
### 4. UPGRADE TO PREMIUM
### =========================
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/users/upgrade
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### =========================
### 5. CHECK USER AGAIN (PREMIUM)
### =========================
GET http://localhost:8080/api/users/currentUser
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### =========================
### 6. MAKE ADMIN
### ⚠️ SOLO SI YA ERES ADMIN
### =========================
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/users/createAdmin/admin
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### =========================
### 7. CHECK USER AGAIN (ADMIN)
### =========================
GET http://localhost:8080/api/users/currentUser
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### =========================
### 8. CREATE DANCE (ADMIN)
### =========================
POST http://localhost:8080/api/dances/save
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Sevillanas8",
  "region": "Andalucía",
  "description": "Baile típico andaluz",
  "videoUrl": "https://youtube.com/test"
}

### =========================
### 9. GET ALL DANCES
### =========================
GET http://localhost:8080/api/dances/all
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### =========================
### 10. GENERATE QUIZ (PREMIUM)
### =========================
GET http://localhost:8080/api/questions/quiz/8
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### =========================
### 11. CHECK ANSWER
### =========================
POST http://localhost:8080/api/questions/check
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "questionId": 10,
  "answer": "A"
}

### =========================
### 12. GET PROGRESS
### =========================
GET http://localhost:8080/api/progress/8
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### =========================
### 13. GET ALL PROGRESS
### =========================
GET http://localhost:8080/api/progress/all
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### =========================
### 14. GLOBAL RANKING
### =========================
GET http://localhost:8080/api/ranking/global
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### =========================
### 15. DANCE RANKING
### =========================
GET http://localhost:8080/api/ranking/dance/8
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}



